Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.21,0:01:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He was last seen in District 8 on the west side.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's within our compound!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your Intelligence Department doing?!
