Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.65,0:02:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate your quick understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,As a member of the same organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.91,0:02:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it is regrettable that we must suspect\Nthe Chief of Operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is pan of our job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.59,0:02:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering the history between me and him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems like the logical step to take.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Take her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been a while, Chairman Kiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.42,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This is quite a rude welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.00,0:02:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I need not apologize to you for the impropriety.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a necessary procedure in order\Nto speak with you at leisure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You certainly haven't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.93,0:02:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my convenience mean nothing then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.48,0:02:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The problem being discussed\Nis an urgent matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It was unavoidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Please understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.78,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's Seele and not the Committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no intention of creating a new god.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We would like your cooperation,\NProfessor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Fuyutsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor! Professor Fuyutsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.75,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\pos(960,335)\3c&H8E8E8E&}YEAR 1999, KYOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor! Professor Fuyutsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna join us for some beer in Kamogawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.17,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryoko and the others are saying\Nthey'll go if you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Our professor was also saying you should\Nshow up once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's good to go out and have\Na drink every so often.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.02,0:03:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You excel at your work,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't take socializing seriously\Nand that's not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.15,0:03:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Fuyutsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.53,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a bioengineering student\Nwho submitted an interesting paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The student's name is Ikari. Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.16,0:03:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari? No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her about you and she said\Nshe was interested in meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll probably contact you eventually,\Nso take care of things, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, was it? All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.80,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz1.398\c&H000014&\pos(953.333,304.334)}Metaphysical Biology Research Room 1 Fuyutsuki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I read your paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.35,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a couple of things questionable,\Nbut it was a stimulating paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui Ikari, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.90,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are your plans for the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to find work?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you intend to join the research lab here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't thought that far ahead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, aren't you forgetting a third option?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm also considering a domestic life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, that's only if I can find someone nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:34.25,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,361.667)}BACK IN THE YEAR 2015
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.30,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With an S2 engine on board,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 01 has become\Nan absolute being!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no use for an actualized god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We must not create a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot allow that man to create a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.86,0:04:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Gendo Ikari, is he a man that can be trusted?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.87,0:04:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gendo Rokubungi? I've heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:00.82,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,357.667)}BACK IN THE YEAR 1999
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I've never met him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's always some rumor\Ngoing around about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.19,Signs,,0,0,0,,Kyoto Prefecture Police Department
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? He asked to be released\Ninto my custody?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.08,0:05:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When should I come over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about you from a certain person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,so I wanted to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a rather coarse man,\Nto get into a drunken brawl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no time to talk.\NThey just picked a fight with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.13,0:05:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very good at being liked,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.26,0:05:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but I am used to being treated coldly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's none of my business anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Fuyutsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you seem to be exactly the person\NI expected you to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.23,0:05:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, my first impression of him was of distaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And back then, seasons and autumn\Nstill existed in this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am seeing Mr. Rokubungi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard that, I wasn't able\Nto hide my surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never would have thought you would\Nshare your time with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.71,0:06:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Professor Fuyutsuki,\Nhe's quite a sweet person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.43,0:06:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that no one knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's more blissful not to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I inconvenience you by\Nintroducing you to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll admit that he's an interesting man,\Nthough I can't get to like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But within our circle, the common opinion\Nwas that he had approached Yui
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for her talent and for\Nthe organization backing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.44,0:06:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, I would hear rumors that this\Norganization was called Seele.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.83,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,347)}YEAR 2000, ANTARCTICA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.19,0:06:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That tragedy occurred in the final year\Nof the 20th century.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:48.51,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,356.333)}YEAR 2001
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And the first year of\Nthe 21st century was pure hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.80,0:06:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no other word to describe that year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:49.43,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,356.333)}YEAR 2002
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,To think this was once a continent of ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.29,0:06:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no trace of it left.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Professor Fuyutsuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd heard that you were a member\Nof the Katsuragi Research Team.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Luckily, I had returned to Japan\Nthe day before the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was able to escape the tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rokubungi, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.58,0:07:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I have a different name now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.84,0:07:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A postcard? Not a business card?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.62,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz341\c&H000009&\pos(907.44,294)}We're Married
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.62,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz341\c&H000009&\pos(1180.469,390.166)}Gendo & Yui\NIkari
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.62,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\frz341\c&H000009&\pos(1078.44,702)}It has been\Na long time.\NAre you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari? Gendo Ikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.04,0:07:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,My wife has been nagging me to get\Nthis to you, Professor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She seems to be a fan of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.59,0:07:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:37.01,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000009&\frz332\fs80\pos(1552.711,-2.75)}Gendo & Yui\NIkari
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:37.01,Sloppy Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H000009&\frz331.7\fs80\pos(1270.576,408.583)}It has been\Na long time.\NAre you doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,How is Yui doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.22,0:07:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she participating in this expedition?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.38,0:07:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui wanted to come, but we\Nhave a child now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:51.20,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz353\c&H000000&\3c&H0894A5&\fs55\pos(650.773,465.168)}SAFETY FIRST
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Your organization... Seele, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard nothing but bad things about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't approve of forcibly\Npinning down the board of directors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fastidious as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No clean organization can survive\Nin this day and age anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The official investigation of the Second Impact...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If the investigation team consisted\Nonly of Seele people,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,you would run into all sons of issues later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.73,0:08:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just a makeshift solution\Nto avoid that, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.51,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,347)}YEAR 2015
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.55,0:08:13.80,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,59)}NERV HEADQUARTERS - ISOLATION FACILITY 4
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't handle dark places very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All the bad memories come flooding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the sole survivor of the original expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.02,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,347)}YEAR 2002
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:27.02,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\c&H834B40&\pos(960,65.667)}SOUTH POLE INVESTIGATION SHIP - ISOLATION FACILITY 2
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.06,0:08:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Misato Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi? She's Dr. Katsuragi's daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she hasn't spoken for\Nalmost two years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It attests to the hell that she witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Her physical injuries have healed,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.95,0:08:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,but psychological wounds do not heal so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:45.71,Signs,,0,0,0,,{\frz353\c&H000000&\3c&H0894A5&\fs55\pos(650.773,465.168)}SAFETY FIRST
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.16,0:08:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't conclude our findings\Nfor our investigation lightly either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.96,0:08:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This giant of light...\NThis incident is full of mysteries.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.04,0:08:55.88,Neutral Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\pos(960,336.6)\c&H000000&\3c&HDDDBD6&\fs60}United Nations Moves Headquarters to Japan\NIn Five Years, Candidate is New Tokyo-2\NSecond Impact Caused by a Massive Meteor\NImpossible to Predict or Avoid\NProbability of Once in Every Several\NHundred Million Years\NOfficial United Nations Statement\NAt 20-30% of the Speed of Light
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon after, the United Nations issued an official statement
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.88,0:08:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,stating that the Second Impact was caused by a massive meteor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.88,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But from where I stood, I could see
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.80,0:09:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,that the information had been\Nblatantly massaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Behind all this was Seele and hints that\Na man named Kiel was involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And it made me want to learn the\Ndark truth of that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.94,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,336.333)}YEAR 2003, HAKONE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if that might eventually lead me to the name of Yui Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:15.15,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\bord2\c&HF3D4DE&\pos(960,765.667)}UNITED NATIONS ARTIFICIAL EVOLUTION LABORATORY
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.15,0:09:16.95,Signs,,0,0,0,,{{\bord2\blur1.5\fs80\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,112.333)\frz359.5}DIRECTOR'S OFFICE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.95,0:09:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you hide the existence\Nof the giant of light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys knew about the\NSecond Impact, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That it would happen on that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That it would happen on that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.29,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs70\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,664.333)}LABORATORY DIRECTOR GENDO IKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.77,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were lucky enough\Nto get out the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it also luck that you took\Nall your research with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am surprised that this material\Nescaped destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I did a thorough investigation of your assets.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.23,0:09:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure raising a child is expensive,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.85,0:09:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,but isn't the amount rather large\Nfor you to have privately?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.81,0:09:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You impress me, Professor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not transfer to the department\Nof economics?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go public about Seele\Nand the Dead Sea Scrolls
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,being secretly behind the Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of letting the people\Nwho caused that get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.16,0:10:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.45,0:10:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But before you do, there is something\NI would like to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going down quite a ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.50,0:10:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.77,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A cavern left behind by someone,\Nwho was not us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Though eighty-nine percent of it is buried.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,An underground cavern that was originally\Na neat spherical shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.44,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All the resources mankind has to offer\Nare being poured into that facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Professor Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Akagi, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.91,0:10:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is the best place to research
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,the fundamental theories for the\Nbio-computers of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.05,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I intend to name it Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Magi? After the three wise men from the East?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.89,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what you wanted to show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.89,0:11:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritsuko, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.94,0:11:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this that giant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.02,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Here at Gehirn, we call that giant Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.40,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But this is not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It is not the original.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is an Eva, made from Adam by man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,An Eva?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Adam Revival Project,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,generally known as Project E,\Nand this is our mockup,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.20,0:11:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Eva Unit 00.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,A Prototype for a god?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,work with me to create a new era\Nin the history of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:45.10,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,347)}YEAR 2015
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry. Let's hurry up and retest Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Miss Katsuragi around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.58,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Misato Katsuragi! Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.24,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs80\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,172.333)}YEAR 2005\NNEW TOKYO-2, NAGANO PREFECTURE
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.74,0:12:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.32,0:12:05.74,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs60\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,400.333)}2ND TOKYO UNIVERSITY, SCHOOL GROUNDS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I met a girl named Katsuragi the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.74,0:12:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Other people will only look at me from afar,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and each time, I am reminded of\Nthe weight your name carries,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,but this girl has no reservation\Ntowards me for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.93,0:12:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I am told that she is the sole survivor\Nof that expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She was apparently aphasic for a time,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but now, she chatters away a mile a minute\Nas if to make up for lost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritchan, I am still burrowed underground,\Nthe same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I've grown tired of the lunches they provide.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,On the surface, they have apparently begun\Nworking on the plans for New Tokyo-S
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,in accordance with the Second\NCapital Transfer Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.83,0:12:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Lately, Misato hadn't been showing up\Nat the university,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and when I finally got her to tell me why,\Nit was so idiotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.42,0:12:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, she had been sleeping with\Nher boyfriend at her apartment,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,for an entire week!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I have seen an unexpected side of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She introduced him to me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:12:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He's good-looking,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.63,0:13:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,but I just cannot get to like his frivolous attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,As I recall, you have never been\Ngood around boys, Ritchan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, being raised only by a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.43,0:13:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry. I have left you to your\Nown devices for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awful of me to act like a mother\Nonly when it's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.24,0:13:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:20.40,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,347)}YEAR 2004
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.90,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs70\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,365.667)}HAKONE - UNDERGROUND LABORATORY 2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,LCL electrified. Pressure at plus zero point two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,No destrudo readings detected in transmissions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.45,BG,,0,0,0,,Para-base is stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this child doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He's Director Ikari's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, this is not a nursery school.\NToday is a crucial day!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Professor Fuyutsuki.\NI'm the one who brought him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yui, this is your experiment today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.46,0:13:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to show my child the bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.28,0:13:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were Ms. Yui's final words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The irregular circumstances erased her\Nfrom this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.77,0:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly as I had wished.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am such a horrible woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Ritchan, Director Ikari changed after that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been for the past week?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're allowed to grieve, but you\Nneed to be aware
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.95,0:14:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are responsible for\Nmore than yourself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki, I am going to recommend\Na new project starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.16,0:14:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already proposed it to Chairman Kiel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.75,0:14:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.55,0:14:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The path to godhood that none have\Never succeeded in before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The Human Instrumentality Project.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.93,0:14:30.89,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,347)}YEAR 2008
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.93,0:14:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,congratulations on the completion of\Nthe fundamental theory of Magi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not exactly a gift to celebrate it with,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but my formal admission into Gehirn\Nhas been unofficially approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.19,0:14:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be working on Project E\Nstarting next month.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.00,0:14:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Technology Development Department,\NRitsuko Akagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's my ID.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.17,0:14:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the command center\Nhad been completed,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,so I came to see it, but this place is a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want the command center,\Nthe Director and Dr. Akagi are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have no regrets concerning my work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.22,0:15:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar! You just can't forget about Ms. Yui, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.11,0:15:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:30.20,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,347)}YEAR 2010
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.20,0:15:31.61,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\pos(955.909,753.75)}GEOFRONT ARTIFICIAL CANOPY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.70,0:15:33.66,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\pos(955.909,769.417)}LOWER LEVEL 2 DIRECT SUPPORT AREA {\fs40}(FUTURE LOCATION)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the headquarters for Gehirn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.66,0:15:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring your child today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but you have a son, if I'm not mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking care of a friend's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.69,0:15:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This girl reminds me of someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.83,0:16:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Yui?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All files concerning Rei Ayanami\Nhave been erased already?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.86,0:16:10.07,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(966.667,800.334)}{\pos(960,785.25)}COMPLETED
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Magi Casper, Magi Balthasar,\Nand Magi Melchior.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.37,0:16:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Magi are the three pans\Nthat make up who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.37,0:16:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The scientist in me, the mother in me,\Nand the woman in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.13,0:16:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And those three elements will be in\Nconstant conflict with one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The three pans of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.73,0:16:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The only thing left is to power it up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to go home early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Misato's coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, I didn't know she\Nwas a member of Gehirn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.85,0:16:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe she's in Germany?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's serving in Branch 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I suppose it's a long-distance relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they broke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, and they looked so good together too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You can never tell with a man and a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's not logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That cool attitude of yours\Ncertainly hasn't changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.00,0:16:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to let your own\Nhappiness slip away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness is even harder to define.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's been a longtime since\NI've gone drinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.13,0:17:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you want something, Rei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I got lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Then you want to\Nleave here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But you won't be able to get home\Nby yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.82,0:17:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business, you old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can go home by myself,\Nso leave me alone, you old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.01,0:17:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not nice to call someone an old hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you are an old hag, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get mad. You need\Na good scolding from Director Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the Director calls you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, “That old hag is pushy,”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.42,0:17:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,or that he, “doesn't need that old hag anymore.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.02,0:18:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He says, “That old hag is pushy,”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,or that he, “doesn't need that old hag anymore.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't need that old hag anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what the Director calls you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you die,\Nyou can always be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Rei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.71,0:18:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The Human Instrumentality Project Committee,\Nchaired by Kiel Lorenz,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.59,0:18:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,dissolved the research organization,\NGehirn, the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And they formed the special duty\Norganization, Nerv,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,as the organization that would\Ncarry out all projects.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us were moved directly into Nerv,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,with the exception of one, Dr. Akagi,\Nthe remarkable creator of the Magi System.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.57,Matisse Sign,,0,0,0,,{\bord2\blur1.5\fs90\3c&H9A9A9A&\pos(960,347)}YEAR 2015
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've put the guards outside to sleep for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.60,0:19:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This will cost you your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to get closer to the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,within myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.21,0:19:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.89,0:19:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the problem has been resolved, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.56,0:19:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.71,0:19:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
