Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've probably put you through a lot of trouble
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.88,0:20:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,by the time you're listening to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell Ritchan I said I'm sorry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.14,0:20:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, since I've troubled you so much anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,there's this flower I've been growing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd make me happy if you'd water it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji knows where it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:21:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Katsuragi, the truth is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Go forward without any hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ever get to see you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.54,0:21:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say the words I wasn't able\Nto say eight years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.54,0:21:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Message recorded at 12:02pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.55,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really such a jerk...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.08,0:21:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right then, all I could do was\Nrun away from Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.21,0:21:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There was nothing I could do or say.\NI was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.09,0:21:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me realize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.46,0:22:00.63,TBC Card,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.07,0:23:06.94,Preview Card,,0,0,0,,PREVIEW
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.94,0:23:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka falls into a psychological pitfall\Ndue to having lost to Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the psychological attack\Nfrom an Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.74,0:23:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,delivers the finishing blow to Asuka's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.78,0:23:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji is unable to offer her\Nany words of comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.00,0:23:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, "At Least, Be Human"
